<h2 id="shadowrocket-for-ios">Shadowrocket for iOS</h2>

<p>下载 <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/shadowrocket/id932747118">Appstore</a></p>

<dl>
  <dt>扫描二维码.</dt>
  <dd>1. 点击左上角扫描图标.</dd>
  <dd>2. 允许shadowrocket相机使用权限.</dd>
  <dd>4. 允许shadowrocket VPN 权限.</dd>
  <dd>5. 点击开启VPN.</dd>
</dl>

<dl>
  <dt>从剪贴板导入.</dt>
  <dd>1. 复制VMess链接到剪贴板.</dd>
  <dd>2. 打开shadowrocket.</dd>
  <dd>4. 添加VMess到列表.</dd>
  <dd>5. 点击开启VPN.</dd>
</dl>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// an example a Shadowrocket format VMess url.</span>
<span class="nx">vmess</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="c1">//Y2hhY2hhMjAtcG9seTEzMDU6YjZiMGJmNWQtZWFjMS00NzM1LThiNDYtNmJlYTYwZTEwZmQwQDEwMGdoazEwMDAxLndlcnNkLnh5ejo0NDM=?remarks=R2VPN&amp;obfsParam=%7B%22Host%22:%22100ghk10101.wgwsd.xyz%22%7D&amp;path=/r2&amp;obfs=websocket&amp;tls=1&amp;peer=100ghk10101.wgwsd.xyz&amp;mux=1&amp;alterId=233</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

