<h2 id="v2rayn-for-windows">V2RayN for Windows</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left">从源站下载</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left"><a href="https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/releases/download/5.29/v2rayN-Core.zip">Github</a></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<ol>
  <li>下载V2RayN并解压.</li>
  <li>双击”v2rayN.exe”打开.</li>
  <li>点击添加VMess或其他方式.</li>
  <li>输入服务器信息保存.</li>
</ol>

