<h2 id="v2ray-for-linux">V2Ray for Linux</h2>

<p>从源站下载 <a href="https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases">Github</a></p>

<dl>
<dt>一行一行执行以下命令</dt>
</dl>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mkdir</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="nb">p</span> <span class="sr">/usr/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mkdir</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="nb">p</span> <span class="sr">/etc/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mkdir</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="nb">p</span> <span class="sr">/var/</span><span class="n">log</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mv</span> <span class="n">v2ray</span> <span class="n">v2ctl</span> <span class="sr">/usr/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mv</span> <span class="n">config</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">json</span> <span class="sr">/etc/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">chmod</span> <span class="o">+</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="sr">/usr/</span><span class="n">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="o">/*</span>
  <span class="n">sudo</span> <span class="n">mv</span> <span class="n">v2ray</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">service</span> <span class="s1">'/etc/systemd/system/v2ray.service'</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<dl>
<dt>替换config.json至以下内容</dt>
</dl>

<div class="language-json highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nl">"log"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="nl">"loglevel"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"warning"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
